      • emitSelectAlternative

        private void emitSelectAlternative(LambdaForm.Name selectAlternativeName,
                         LambdaForm.Name invokeBasicName)
        Emit bytecode for the selectAlternative idiom. The pattern looks like (Cf. MethodHandleImpl.makeGuardWithTest): Lambda(a0:L,a1:I)=>{ t2:I=foo.test(a1:I); t3:L=MethodHandleImpl.selectAlternative(t2:I,(MethodHandle(int)int),(MethodHandle(int)int)); t4:I=MethodHandle.invokeBasic(t3:L,a1:I);t4:I}
        Parameters:
        selectAlternativeName -
        invokeBasicName -
